Uses of Package
net.krotscheck.dfr

  • Packages that use net.krotscheck.dfr 
    Package Description
    net.krotscheck.dfr
    Data file stream converters.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.bson
    BSON Data file encoders and decoders.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.csv
    CSV Data file encoders and decoders.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.filter.column
    A data filter that only permits a subset of columns.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.json
    JSON Data file encoders and decoders.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.stream
    Data converters for file formats that are binary or require an input stream.
    net.krotscheck.dfr.text
    Data converters for file formats that are text based.
  • Classes in net.krotscheck.dfr used by net.krotscheck.dfr 
    Class and Description
    AbstractFilteredDataStream
    An abstract implementation of the data encoder, to consolidate some common functionality and provide a simple extension point.
    IDataDecoder
    This interface describes a data decoder, which attempts to convert a table-based file into an iterable key/value map.
    IDataEncoder
    This interface describes a data encoder, which accepts rows of data and writes them to a specific file format.
    IDataFilter
    This interface describes a data filter, allowing custom transformations on data streams.
    IFilteringDataStream
    This interface describes a data stream (whether a converter, encoder or decoder) that is capable of filtering its throughput.
    Type
    A list of value types that can be casting purpose.
